title: Madina Lake: Attics To Eden
description:
MADINA LAKE: ATTICS TO EDEN

That's right! Madina Lake's newest album.

I apologise for the low bitrate, but it's the best that's out there on the web. And it still sounds awesome.

Also included is the Never Take Us Alive single, which includes an acoustic version of the song.
